.000Z","msg":"點注意法？<br />\n因為我其實唔點食炸野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:08:51.000Z","msg":"1.少吃生冷食物：<br />\n吃過量會讓脾胃虛寒，造成消化不良而脹氣或拉肚子。<br />\n<br />\n2.避免攝取易產氣的食物：<br />\n包括：豆類、豆製品、花椰菜、洋蔥、地瓜、奶類、碳酸飲料等，吃太多易造成脹氣。<br />\n<br />\n3.少吃甜食：<br />\n蛋糕、甜甜圈、糖果等甜食，吃起來甜滋滋的，但都屬於精緻糖類食物，中醫認為吃太多甜食容易造成腸胃濕滯，加重消化不良的症狀。<br />\n<br />\n4.飲食細嚼慢嚥：<br />\n習慣以快速度吃完東西、為了趕時間而狼吞虎嚥，或是邊吃邊說話，這些飲食習慣都會在過程中比一般人吃進更多的空氣，更容易造成腸道發出咕嚕咕嚕的聲音。"},{"pid":"908689175a3e94dc5d30167b967b7f9eafa24db6","tid":1783381,"uid":251769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:12:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推，今日既行動post</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a77EG51.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa77EG51.jpg&h=a86f9171&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z7yo8L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ7yo8L2.jpg&h=242df1ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SmC9jSP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSmC9jSP.jpg&h=8bedeaeb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7c2fb9bafb2bee80284f35f14e1891b3d40482c3","tid":1783381,"uid":203797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5209f3ab5aee24d3aad5a5e91695fca04c82bb52","tid":1783381,"uid":209657,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"係咪我條腸有細菌 好驚"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:14:40.000Z","msg":"唔洗擔心 你條腸一定有細菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n普通細菌同益菌balance好就冇事"},{"pid":"1cf39d025c6a75a4abe534f25abb743cfc92feaf","tid":1783381,"uid":255450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T18:14:41.000Z","msg":"肚風多，可試吓飲薑水，或者去濕茶"},{"pid":"7b960e2582230a7a5df1ba5b0dbce17aa1f07df0","tid":1783381,"uid":152222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"667626c871a8048f49650683586427b764afc003","tid":1783381,"uid":75267,"like":7